WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.004
Keyingi tushunchalarda

00:00:02.004 --> 00:00:07.544
biz qanday qilib notatsiya bilan oraliqni hisoblash haqida o‘rganganlarimizni birlashtirmoqchimiz.

00:00:07.544 --> 00:00:11.699
Ushbu videoning maqsadi oraliqni hisoblashni qayta o‘rganish emas

00:00:11.699 --> 00:00:17.114
balki siz allaqachon bilgan o‘lchovdan foydalanib notatsiyani tanishtirishdir.

00:00:17.114 --> 00:00:21.710
Keling kimningdir saytimizda sarflagan minutlarini hisobga olaylik.

00:00:21.710 --> 00:00:26.219
Tasavvur qiling biz besh individualning saytimizda sarflagan vaqt miqdorini to‘playmiz.

00:00:26.219 --> 00:00:27.899
Oxirgi videodan,

00:00:27.899 --> 00:00:30.905
biz qiymatlarni ushbu usulda belgilashimizni ko‘rdik,

00:00:30.905 --> 00:00:33.140
x1 birinchi qiymat uchun,

00:00:33.140 --> 00:00:35.210
x2 ikkinchi qiymat uchun,

00:00:35.210 --> 00:00:38.659
x3 uchinchi qiymat uchun va. hokazo.

00:00:38.659 --> 00:00:42.030
Tasavvur qiling biz dastlabki ikki raqamni birgalikda qo‘shishni xohlaymiz.

00:00:42.030 --> 00:00:47.969
Biz notatsiyaga misoldagi 15 plus 10 ga o‘xshash,

00:00:47.969 --> 00:00:51.159
x1 plus x2 ni yozamiz.

00:00:51.159 --> 00:00:54.229
Agar biz ikkitadan ortiq qiymatni qo‘shishni xohlaganimizda,

00:00:54.229 --> 00:00:57.920
bir xil jarayonni takrorlash zerikarli bo‘lardi.

00:00:57.920 --> 00:01:00.469
Tasavvur qiling bizda 100 ta qiymat bor.

00:01:00.469 --> 00:01:05.239
Bizda a, x1 plus x2 plus x3

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:10.545
plus bo‘lardi va biz shu jarayonni x 100 gacha davom ettirardik.

00:01:10.545 --> 00:01:14.150
Kimdir buni birlashtirishning yaxshiroq yo‘lini topgan bo‘lsa kerak.

00:01:14.150 --> 00:01:17.000
Yaxshiroq yo‘li borligi ko‘rinib turibdi.

